* [http://plato.stanford.edu/entries/liberalism/ 斯坦福哲学百科全书对自由主义的定义] 由 Gerald F. Gaus
* [http://fcis.oise.utoronto.ca/~daniel_schugurensky/assignment1/1935dewey.html On John Dewey's 自由主義和社會行動]
* [https://web.archive.org/web/20060827212411/http://www.wilsoncenter.org/index.cfm?fuseaction=wq.print&essay_id=8468&stoplayout=true Peter Berkowitz 對“現代自由主義”]
* [https://web.archive.org/web/20070203033757/http://cepa.newschool.edu/het/schools/frenchlib.htm 18和19世紀法國的自由主義]
* [https://web.archive.org/web/20080222205641/http://ark.cdlib.org/ark:/13030/ft4w10063f/ 自由主義是什麼，政治理論家Ronald Beiner的評論文章]
* [http://jeffryfisher.net/Statesman/History/Liberal.htm 美國與英國對“自由主義”一詞的定義差別，Jeffry Fischer]
* [http://www.mises.org/liberal.asp 自由主義計畫]，[[路德維希·馮·米塞斯|路德維希·馮·米塞斯]]
* [https://web.archive.org/web/20110211151351/http://www.liberal-international.org/editorial.asp?ia_id=535 1947年牛津宣言]
* [http://www.mises.org/story/1957 自由主義對抗法西斯主義] by Roderick T. Long

